-- Twitter Acquires Posterous to Add Staff Adept at Photo Sharing
-- B y   B r i a n   W o m a c k
-- 2012-03-12T21:18:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-12/twitter-acquires-posterous-adding-staff-adept-at-web-video-photo-sharing.html
Twitter Inc., the microblogging
service, said it acquired Posterous, a website that specializes
in online photo and video sharing.  “Today we are welcoming a very talented group from
Posterous to Twitter,” San Francisco-based Twitter said in a
blog posting. “This team has built an innovative product that
makes sharing across the Web and mobile devices simple -- a goal
we share.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
